sequenceDiagram
  participant F as Frontend Forum UI
  participant G as Gateway
  participant FS as Forum Service
  participant US as User Service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant AN as Analytics Service

  F->>G: POST /api/forums/:id/threads/:threadId/posts
  G->>FS: create post
  FS->>US: verify token
  US-->>FS: userId
  FS->>DB: insert ForumPost
  FS->>AN: emit POST_CREATED
  FS-->>F: post payload

  F->>G: POST /api/forums/:id/threads/:threadId/posts/:postId/reactions
  G->>FS: react to post
  FS->>DB: upsert ForumPostReaction
  FS->>AN: emit POST_REACTED
  FS-->>F: reaction summary
